<core:FragmentDefinition xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form" xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" class="sapUiSizeCompact" xmlns:tnt="sap.tnt"
    xmlns:c="zui3derp.control" xmlns:t="sap.ui.table">
    <Panel expandable="false" expanded="true" width="100%" class="sapUiNoContentPadding sapUiSizeCompact">
        <Toolbar height="3rem" style="Clear">
            <Label text=""/>
            <ToolbarSpacer />
            <!-- <Button text="Upload" icon="sap-icon://upload" press="onAddFile"/> -->
            <Button text="Delete Selected" press="onDeleteFile" visible="{= ${FilesEditModeModel>/editMode} === true ? true : false }"/>
            <Button type="Ghost" icon="sap-icon://edit" text="Edit" press="setFilesEditMode" visible="{= ${FilesEditModeModel>/editMode} === true ? false : true }"/>
            <Button type="Ghost" icon="sap-icon://decline" text="Cancel" press="cancelFilesEdit" visible="{= ${FilesEditModeModel>/editMode} === true ? true : false }"/>
        </Toolbar>
        
        <VBox id="FilesBox">
            <UploadCollection id="UploadCollection" instantUpload="false"></UploadCollection>
            <!-- <UploadCollection id="UploadCollection2"></UploadCollection> -->
        </VBox>
    </Panel>
</core:FragmentDefinition>        